title: Best Bits with Morgan and Special Guest Amy: PART 1
itunes:title: Best Bits with Morgan and Special Guest Amy: PART 1
description:
Morgan and Amy discuss their worst date stories, plus the careers they dreamed of having as kids. They each share the story of how they joined The Bobby Bones Show. Amy talks about mom life and how she’s doing with her kids back at school, and she answers Morgan’s rapid fire questions.

 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
